title: 820-00239 No power
message:
This mac has been repaired by another technician in the U9300 region.  
The mac displays backlight on and then quickly powers off.  Shows USB activity for a few seconds.
I replaced UB300, as it had oxidized components around it. 



Voltage: 
PP3V3_G3H 3,4V
PP5V_S0 starts with 5V and drops to 300mV
PPBUS 13,07V
PP3V3_S5 3,35V
PP3V3_SUS 3.35V for a few seconds.
